{"tid":1524900,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"拆黨鐵 好可能弊多過利","createTime":"2019-08-31T18:39:19.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-01T03:47:53.000Z","uid":236709,"like":21,"dislike":96,"uniUserReply":49,"replies":[{"pid":"2cc49f083b0b44efa0d3fedcddce3e5e62e477a9","tid":1524900,"uid":236709,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T18:39:19.000Z","msg":"雖然黨鐵今日係真係非常之仆街<br />\n但如果聽日拆站嘅話<br />\n就畀足理由黨鐵玩封站<br />\n到時聽日嘅手足就未必可以周圍be water<br />\n<br />\n而且到時政府就大條道理入示威者阻住社會運作<br />\n又話9月開學乜乜乜地鐵壞咗大家唔方便<br />\n<br />\nSorry我真係潑咗冷水<br />\n我都知大家眼火爆<br />\n但拆黨鐵呢樣嘢的確發洩多個有利<br />\n<br />\n一係呢就拆佢總部<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n一係呢就君子報仇十年未晚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n總之個人認為依加時機唔啱啦"},{"pid":"53c1d525b3843bb9b845ab094950ca61a056f968","tid":1524900,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T18:39:25.000Z","msg":"我知大家好撚嬲, 因為我地冇清算黨鐵先搞到今日咁, 但係要記得今日要去春袋報仇, 黨鐵黎緊一齊再清算！香港人加油 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Lz7uo3t.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLz7uo3t.jpg&h=4ed7d51c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n九月一號下午一點機場見<br />\n<br />\n901機場和你塞 Channel<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyou&d=N1Uxy2NPgyNkiLrD4Rz70r32HZRMtn4xjJY4gFhUisg%3D&h=fa3b98ab\" target=\"_blank\">http://t.me/stuckwithyou</a><br />\n901機場和你塞 公海<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyouopen\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyouopen&d=N1Uxy2NPgyNkiLrD4Rz70r32HZRMtn4xjJY4gFhUisg%3D&h=933bcd07\" target=\"_blank\">http://t.me/stuckwithyouopen</a><br />\n901機場和你塞 宣傳<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyoupromote\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyoupromote&d=N1Uxy2NPgyNkiLrD4Rz70r32HZRMtn4xjJY4gFhUisg%3D&h=643b20c2\" target=\"_blank\">http://t.me/stuckwithyoupromote</a>"},{"pid":"d8602374fa5